<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall abolish, in respect of the natural persons and undertakings covered by title I of the general programme for the abolition of restrictions on freedom of establishment, hereinafter called "beneficiaries &ldquo;, the restrictions referred to in title III of this programme affecting the right to take up and pursue self-employed activities in the classes of insurance specified in Article 1 of the first coordination Directive. </inglise>
