<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall amend their national regulations in accordance with this Directive and within 18 months of the notification of the first coordination Directive and shall forthwith inform the Commission thereof. </inglise>
